Here you can see how we spent our summer last year. ğŸ˜„ (to be honest this summer is not that different, but we're now sitting in an office instead of our basementğŸ˜‚). On May 12th 2020, we appeared on the biggest startup TV show in Austria. At that time, we didn't have a single ready assembled REELOQ in stock, because our producer had to shut down the factory for 2 months due to corona. That's why we only had all the individual parts of our REELOQ. We thought that there would be a maximum of 50 mountaineers among the viewers of the TV show and we watched our broadcast almost relaxed (or as relaxed you can be when you see your face on TV!! ğŸ˜±). Only a few hours later, we were completely sold out and didn't know how we should cope with the incredible amount of orders. With every new order that came in, we got even more nervous. But still: we had to get to work and assemble our beloved REELOQs. ğŸ”¨ For weeks we sat in our basement and, with the help of the best friends and family we could think of, assembled more than a thousand REELOQs ourselves until our manufacturer was able to deliver again. ğŸ˜… Those were really exhausting weeks that we definitely didn't expect, but in retrospect it's a funny memory and an important part of our big adventure. We are already excited about the unexpected twists and turns that are yet to come! Stay tuned. ğŸ’¥ ğŸ‘
